extends layout

block content
  h1 API IMAGE SEARCH ABSTRACTION LAYER
  h2 User stories:
  p 1. I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
  p 2. I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
  p 3. I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings.
  br
  h2 Example usage:
  code https://anya92-imagesearch.herokuapp.com/search/katowice
  br
  code https://anya92-imagesearch.herokuapp.com/search/warsaw?offset=5
  br
  h2 Examle output:
  code {title: "Katowice", url: "https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5628/22269413059_c3a9af3ed1.jpg", context: "https://www.flickr.com/photos/130058842@N06/22269413059"}, <br> {title: "Katowice", url: "https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7787/29887551112_cb3bc3f361.jpg", context: "https://www.flickr.com/photos/130058842@N06/29887551112"}, ...
  br
  h2 Example usage:
  code https://anya92-imagesearch.herokuapp.com/latest
  br
  h2 Examle output:
  code {term: "cracow", when: "2017-01-12T11:15:02.020Z"}, {term: "warsaw", when: "2017-01-12T11:11:17.752Z"}, ...
